76
00:05:38,900 --> 00:05:40,420
Who are you talking about?

77
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:42,140
Miss Xue?

78
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:44,140
If she isn't Zhuang Yunqiu,

79
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:48,220
