84
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:08,420
What?

85
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:10,140
You think they're the same person?

86
00:06:12,140 --> 00:06:13,340
I'm not sure.

87
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:18,160
But I can't shake the feeling
that she's hiding a lot of secrets.

88
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:33,859
I heard there was quite a commotion

89
00:06:33,860 --> 00:06:35,219
