whose reputation is in ruins.

128
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:26,140
Lily.

129
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:28,460
Lily.

130
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:29,940
Lily, don't go!

131
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:30,820
Lily!

132
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:32,580
Lily!

133
00:09:34,060 --> 00:09:35,460
Come back!

134
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:36,740
Come back!

135
00:09:43,180 --> 00:09:44,140
Later,

136
00:09:44,460 --> 00:09:45,620
